1008
01:20:17,445 --> 01:20:19,322
Did you get your car fixed?

1009
01:20:19,739 --> 01:20:22,367
l got a personal letter
from Lee lacocca.

1010
01:20:24,118 --> 01:20:26,788
l did.
They fixed everything for nothing.

1011
01:20:27,247 --> 01:20:28,414
